@startuml Fase2_VistaImplantacao

title Fase 2 - Vista de Implantacao (Ambiente Desenvolvimento)

skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam linetype ortho

node "Maquina Local do Utilizador" as Host {

  node "Browser\nlocalhost:5173" as Browser {
    component "SPA React" as Client
  }

  node "Frontend Dev Server\nVite" as Frontend {
    component "Servidor estatico + HMR" as Vite
  }

  node "Backend Server\nASP.NET Core" as Backend {
    component "SimuladorClinico.Api" as ApiProc
    component "Application + Domain" as Core
    component "In-Memory Session Store" as MemStore
  }
}

cloud "Servico LLM Externo" as LlmCloud

Client --> Vite : carrega aplicacao
Client --> ApiProc : chamadas REST /api/simulacoes/*
ApiProc --> Core : fluxo de simulacao
Core --> MemStore : persistencia temporaria
Core --> LlmCloud : inferencia de respostas

note bottom of Backend
Em producao, substituir in-memory store por persistencia duravel.
end note

@enduml
